- Use descriptive column names
- Set explicit state before assertions
- Verify both visible and hidden states

[Common Patterns & Examples > Chart Interaction Pattern]

```typescript
import { test, expect } from '@fixtures/index.fixtures';

test('interact with chart', async ({ dashboard }) => {
	const columnBar = dashboard('Dashboard Name').getColumnChartWidget('Chart Widget');

	// Legend interaction
	await columnBar.toggleLegendItem('Awaiting Development');
	await columnBar.assertLegendItemDisabled('Awaiting Development');

	// Data point interaction
	await columnBar.clickFirstDataPointForDrillthrough();

	// Verify drillthrough
	await expect(page).toHaveURL(/.*\/drillthrough/);
});
```

**Key points:**

- Use legend item names, not indices
- Target chart elements by CSS classes
- Avoid clicking on data labels with specific values

[Common Patterns & Examples > Error Handling Pattern]

```typescript
import { test, expect } from '@fixtures/index.fixtures';

test('handle validation errors', async ({ page, loginPage }) => {
	// Trigger error
	await loginPage.submitWithInvalidData({
		email: 'invalid-email',
		password: '',
	});

	// Verify error messages
	await expect(loginPage.locator.messageErrorEmail).toBeVisible();
	await expect(loginPage.locator.messageErrorPassword).toBeVisible();

	// Verify form not submitted
	await expect(page).toHaveURL(/.*\/login/);
});
```

**Key points:**

- Test both happy and error paths
- Verify specific error messages
- Ensure form doesn't submit with invalid data

[Common Patterns & Examples > Waiting for Dynamic Content]

```typescript
import { test, expect } from '@fixtures/index.fixtures';

test('wait for dynamic content', async ({ page }) => {
	// Trigger action that loads content
	await page.locator('#load-data-button').click();

	// Wait for loading indicator to disappear
	await expect(page.locator('.loading-spinner')).toBeHidden();

	// Wait for content to appear
	await expect(page.locator('.data-table')).toBeVisible();

	// Verify content loaded
	await expect(page.locator('.data-table tr')).toHaveCount(10);
});
```

**Key points:**

- Wait for loading indicators to disappear
- Wait for content elements to appear
- Use specific conditions, not timeouts

